{"tid":1072712,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"咁可以點","createTime":"2019-03-22T07:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T07:52:23.000Z","uid":55091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"83746f44a5ea54e4520012f46616073c10342a69","tid":1072712,"uid":55091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:43:11.000Z","msg":"今日落街見到公園長櫈有部錄音機<br />\n不斷重複播緊類似唱衰一個機構嘅謾罵<br />\n我好奇走近部錄音機<br />\n發覺有張紙夾咗係錄音機同長櫈之間<br />\n係我想睇吓張紙嘅時候<br />\n有位女士啤住我<br />\n然後我知道我應該要走啦<br />\n係我臨離開佢視線邊緣嘅時候<br />\n佢同我大聲講咗句<br />\n「若要人不知 除非己莫為」<br />\n我有少少難過<br />\n咁又可以點？<br />\n佢除咗係街唱衰人<br />\n佢又可以點?<br />\n佢應該做唔到其他更好方法<br />\n<br />\n咁可以點"},{"pid":"dd94c74c61179afde8ad095617231bc84d6727c2","tid":1072712,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:45:53.000Z","msg":"人體大自爆"},{"pid":"232ab7ad1527492b9c213faac3a0dfe4396324f5","tid":1072712,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd94c74c61179afde8ad095617231bc84d6727c2","tid":1072712,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:45:53.000Z","msg":"人體大自爆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec527559ae2adaac16b8fd99404e52469a147331","tid":1072712,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"232ab7ad1527492b9c213faac3a0dfe4396324f5","tid":1072712,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd94c74c61179afde8ad095617231bc84d6727c2","tid":1072712,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:45:53.000Z","msg":"人體大自爆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:52:23.000Z","msg":"認同分享，謝謝！"}]}